Titolo: Buffy the Vampire Slayer (2002 video game)

Anno: 2002

Descrizione: Buffy the Vampire Slayer is an action beat 'em up video game addition to the Buffy the Vampire Slayer franchise. It is the second video game of the franchise to be released, though the earliest in terms of setting and the first for a console. The novella and dialogue of the game were written by Christopher Golden and Thomas Sniegoski, with additional dialogue provided by Richard Hare.



Genere: Action 

Valutazione: N/A
